Enum StatusCode

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<StatusCode>
public enum StatusCode
extends Enum<StatusCode>

Value range for the client's states, like Connect and Disconnect. These are low level states used in IPhotonPeerListener.peerStatusCallback().
